WEBVTT

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:31.536
to forced migrant labor
and to colonialism.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:34.360
Whites were largely unscathed.

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:36.896
As health professionals,

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:40.176
our tools were pitifully weak:

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:44.056
imploring people to change
their individual behaviors,

00:04:44.080 --> 00:04:46.936
use condoms, reduce number of partners.

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:49.560
Infection rates climbed,

00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:54.176
and when treatment
became available in the West,

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:56.616
treatment that remains
our most potent weapon

00:04:56.640 --> 00:04:58.336
against this virus,

00:04:58.360 --> 00:05:02.736
it was unaffordable
to the public sector across Africa.